item.title: How Do I Host My Server ? [508]
item.dc:creator: @Jordiescape Jordiescape
item.description:
@Jordiescape wrote:

Why are compilers so hard to use?

@echo off "C:\Program Files\Java\YOURJDK\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause
Done. Just go to the path in the compiler to find your JDK version. Here is what I have; JDK1.6.0_07.
